title: [FSX] RealAir DukeV2 (RIP)
description:
Hi guys! I've been a long time leecher of this Pirate Bay Flight Sim community and I wanted to make an attempt to contribute something.

Im not 100% sure this will work, so don't be upset if it doesn't. I tried to the best of my ability to round up all of the V2 files after install. Now I've had the original installed for many years and it was hard to tell whether some files came from the new or old version. I made the best attempt I could.

If this doesn't work, I can upload the installer for someone to crack. Anyways, enjoy!
